57
00:05:48,570 --> 00:05:50,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Matahari terbit di pagi hari.</font>

58
00:05:51,930 --> 00:05:53,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi bulan di malam hari!</font>

59
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:58,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Bayangkan jika matahari terus bersinar.</font>

60
00:06:00,490 --> 00:06:01,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa hidup seperti itu!</font>

61
00:06:01,890 --> 00:06:04,950
