69
00:06:57,580 --> 00:07:00,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, dan apa kau dengar?</font>

70
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:04,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Suami Gyung Hee diserang di tempat parkir,
