101
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sangat menyedihkan.</font>

102
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sangat cantik, dia harus mendapatkan suami baru.</font>

103
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi bagaimana dengan...</font>

104
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:36,450
