108
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:48,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, dan apa kau dengar?</font>

109
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:51,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada pembantu baru di rumah tuan Ahn.</font>

110
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Istri barunya membawanya masuk ke rumah.</font>

111
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,830
