132
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:21,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau peduli?</font>

133
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:23,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Pulanglah!</font>

134
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

135
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:25,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku tidak bisa!</font>

136
00:10:26,270 --> 00:10:29,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika kau memberiku 2 juta dolar?
Lalu aku akan pergi.</font>

137
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:30,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya untuk saat ini saja.</font>

138
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:32,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan pulang jika kau memberikannya.</font>

139
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi!</font>

140
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin bertemu kalian semua.</font>

141
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Selalu saja menyuruhku pergi.</font>

142
