143
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, apa kau lapar?</font>

144
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:54,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? "Hei"?</font>

145
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:58,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat.</font>

146
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebelumnya kau belum pernah menjadi pembantu?</font>

147
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:03,180
