<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bingung.</font>

149
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Setidaknya kau harus tahu posisimu bahkan jika kau tidak mengerti.</font>

150
00:11:06,970 --> 00:11:08,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tidak menonton TV?</font>

151
00:11:08,490 --> 00:11:11,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak menghubungi atasanmu, "Hei."</font>

152
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti gila.</font>

153
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu bagaimana aku harus menghubungimu?</font>

154
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,390
