155
00:11:17,890 --> 00:11:19,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak sesuai denganmu.</font>

156
00:11:19,810 --> 00:11:21,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Wanita!</font>

157
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tutup mulutmu kecuali jika kau ingin ditendang keluar!</font>

158
00:11:24,050 --> 00:11:26,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

159
00:11:27,170 --> 00:11:28,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau lapar?</font>

160
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:37,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang kau membayarnya untuk menyakiti Park Bok Ja.</font>

161
00:11:38,930 --> 00:11:40,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong kosong!</font>

162
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita menemuinya sekarang juga.</font>

163
00:11:42,710 --> 00:11:44,310
