745
00:53:57,010 --> 00:54:03,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena aku tidak memiliki kekuatan, semua
anakmu berpikiran rendah padaku.</font>

746
00:54:04,250 --> 00:54:05,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku minta maaf.</font>

747
00:54:07,970 --> 00:54:09,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemana kau pergi?</font>

748
00:54:10,190 --> 00:54:11,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Silakan tidur.</font>

749
00:54:12,190 --> 00:54:14,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menunggu sampai kau kembali.</font>

750
00:54:15,430 --> 00:54:18,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak perlu, aku tidak mood.</font>

751
00:54:19,030 --> 00:54:21,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bertindak seperti itu.</font>

752
00:54:21,880 --> 00:54:23,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidur saja.</font>

753
00:54:59,190 --> 00:55:01,860
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Makanlah jika kau mengalami masa sulit.</i></font>

754
00:55:02,300 --> 00:55:04,030
