788
00:56:39,170 --> 00:56:40,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lelah, keluarlah.</font>

789
00:56:51,290 --> 00:56:53,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin berbicara denganmu di telepon.</font>

790
00:57:05,880 --> 00:57:07,260
